message.body: Yo! We are thinking of heading to ###### for#####'s grillout Apr 27 weekend...would you all be around by chance? I miss you!
Hey! I just saw the invite. We went last year and I *think* we're free this year (lots of travel in April!). But if you're coming we'll do our best!!!!
Cool :) I think we're going to book today, I'd love to see you!
Excellent! Let me know the details when you have em! xoxox

Ahh that's so exciting!! Let's pow wow about activities soon!
